Package: imergr
Type: Package
Title: Download and Process NASA GPM IMERG Half-Hourly Precipitation Data
Version: 0.0.900
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Ousmane", "Ouedraogo",
      email = "oousmane@proton.me",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides tools to download NASA GPM IMERG (Integrated
    Multi-satellitE Retrievals for GPM) half-hourly precipitation data
    from the NASA Precipitation Processing System (PPS) GIS server
    <https://jsimpsonhttps.pps.eosdis.nasa.gov>. Supports Early and Late
    run products (V07B), converts GeoTIFF outputs to CF-1.7 compliant
    NetCDF files, and provides utilities for credential management and
    batch downloading.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
URL: https://github.com/oousmane/imergr
